<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>InviteFetcher</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background-color: #1F2B3D;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        
        .navbar-logo {
            color: #7289DA;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .navbar-button {
            background-color: #7289DA;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .content {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #1F2B3D;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .content-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        
        .content-title span {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .content-subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .content-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .blue-button {
            background-color: #7289DA;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #1F2B3D;
            padding: 10px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content-title {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .content-subtitle {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .content-description {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
        
        .card {
            background-color: #7289DA;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-title {
           font-size: 24px;
           font-weight: bold;
        }

        .card-description {
           font-size: 16px;
        }

        .release-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #FF5252, #FF4081, #E040FB, #7C4DFF, #536DFE, #448AFF);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .release-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="release-banner">
        <p class="release-message">Official release of the InviteFetcher beta!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a class="navbar-logo" href="/">InviteFetcher</a>
        <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
        <a class="navbar-button" href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
        <% } else { %>
        <a class="navbar-button" href="/login">Login</a>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
    <h1 class="content-title" style="text-align: left;">Build a better <span style="color: blue;">Discord server.</span></h1>
    <p class="content-description" style="font-size: 18px; text-align: left;">InviteFetcher is a powerful Discord bot which offers many features such as invite tracking, giveaway, messages tracking and much more.</p>
    <button class="blue-button" onclick="location.href='/dashboard'">Start tracking invites!</button>
</div>
    
        <div class="content" style="background-color: #1F2B3D;">
    <h2 class="content-subtitle" style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: blue;">Start tracking invites fast.</h2>
    <p class="content-description" style="font-size: 18px;">InviteFetcher is the only bot you will ever need to track invites without worrying about it.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3 class="card-title">Multifunction</h3>
    <p class="card-description">InviteFetcher is offering a bunch of features, not only invite tracking. You will be able to schedule giveaways, reward members, and more.</p>
</div>
    
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Made with ❤️ by cheraphdev</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>